entry.value: SELECT lr.created_on as loanValueDate, lr.created_on as loanMatDate, CONVERT(lr.member_id,CHAR) as customerId, lr.code as loanReferenceID, "Neostream " as accountOfficer, 'KES' as currency, CONVERT(lr.loan_product_id,CHAR) as chargeCode, CONVERT(lr.receiver_account_id ,CHAR) as drawDownAccount, CONVERT(SUM(lf.rate),CHAR) AS chargeAmount, CONVERT(lf.loan_product_id,CHAR) AS ChargeCode, TIMESTAMPDIFF(MONTH,lr.created_on, expected_completion_date) AS loanTerm, CONVERT(lr.principal_amount,CHAR) AS transactionAmount FROM mobifarm.loan_requests lr LEFT JOIN loan_fees lf ON lr.loan_product_id=lf.loan_product_id WHERE lr.sent_to_oracle=0 GROUP BY lf.loan_product_id,lr.id

SELECT a.f_name as firstName , a.l_name as lastName, a.id as customerSetupId, a.loan_account_id as accountSetupId, a.id_no as customerIdNumber, a.phone_number as phoneNumber, a.email as email, 'a' as t24AccountNumber,'b' as t24CustomerNo,a.unique_id as alternateAccountRef FROM mobifarm.users a WHERE a.sent_to_oracle = 0 order by id DESC ;
UPDATE mobifarm.users SET sent_to_oracle = 1 WHERE id= '${customerSetupId}'

INSERT INTO MOBIGROW.TBL_T24_CUSTOMERS (CUSTOMER_ID, CUSTOMER_SETUP_ID, ACCOUNT_SETUP_ID, ALTERNATE_ACCOUNT_REF, CUSTOMER_ID_NUMBER, PHONE_NUMBER, FIRST_NAME, LAST_NAME, EMAIL, T24_ACCOUNT_NUMBER, T24_CUSTOMER_NO, CREATED_AT) VALUES(${now():toNumber()}, '${customerSetupId}', '${accountSetupId}', '${alternateAccountRef}', '${customerIdNumber}', '${phoneNumber}', '${firstName}', '${lastName}', '${email}', '', '', '')
